{"type":"message","id":"1c7800e6","parentId":"caeeeb6e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:03:59.484Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_a185d6098af24ed1a941c2ee","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\r\n\"\"\"\r\nEconomic Calendar Fetcher using FMP API\r\nRetrieves economic events and data releases for specified date range\r\n\"\"\"\r\n\r\nimport argparse\r\nimport json\r\nimport os\r\nimport sys\r\nimport urllib.error\r\nimport urllib.parse\r\nimport urllib.request\r\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\r\nfrom typing import Optional\r\n\r\n\r\ndef get_api_key() -> Optional[str]:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    Get FMP API key from environment variable.\r\n\r\n    Returns:\r\n        API key string or None if not found\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    api_key = os.environ.get(\"FMP_API_KEY\")\r\n    if not api_key:\r\n        print(\"Warning: FMP_API_KEY environment variable not set\", file=sys.stderr)\r\n    return api_key\r\n\r\n\r\ndef fetch_economic_calendar(from_date: str, to_date: str, api_key: str) -> list[dict]:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    Fetch economic calendar data from FMP API.\r\n\r\n    Args:\r\n        from_date: Start date in YYYY-MM-DD format\r\n        to_date: End date in YYYY-MM-DD format\r\n        api_key: FMP API key\r\n\r\n    Returns:\r\n        List of economic event dictionaries\r\n\r\n    Raises:\r\n        urllib.error.HTTPError: If API request fails\r\n        ValueError: If response is invalid\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    base_url = \"https://financialmodelingprep.com/api/v3/economic_calendar\"\r\n\r\n    # Build query parameters\r\n    params = {\"from\": from_date, \"to\": to_date}\r\n\n[210 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774573439477}}
{"type":"message","id":"8b52df23","parentId":"1c7800e6","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:04:02.083Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我看看完整的 URL 构建，可能是 endpoint 已经变更了。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_61f7a7204bdd4cf5b95ee1f3","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.claude\\skills\\claude-trading-skills\\skills\\economic-calendar-fetcher\\scripts\\get_economic_calendar.py","limit":50,"offset":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":314,"output":78,"cacheRead":34889,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35281,"cost":{"input":0.0001884,"output":0.0001716,"cacheRead":0.00383779,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00419779}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774573439486}}
{"type":"message","id":"b0033461","parentId":"8b52df23","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:04:02.096Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_61f7a7204bdd4cf5b95ee1f3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\ndef fetch_economic_calendar(from_date: str, to_date: str, api_key: str) -> list[dict]:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    Fetch economic calendar data from FMP API.\r\n\r\n    Args:\r\n        from_date: Start date in YYYY-MM-DD format\r\n        to_date: End date in YYYY-MM-DD format\r\n        api_key: FMP API key\r\n\r\n    Returns:\r\n        List of economic event dictionaries\r\n\r\n    Raises:\r\n        urllib.error.HTTPError: If API request fails\r\n        ValueError: If response is invalid\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n    base_url = \"https://financialmodelingprep.com/api/v3/economic_calendar\"\r\n\r\n    # Build query parameters\r\n    params = {\"from\": from_date, \"to\": to_date}\r\n\r\n    # Construct URL with parameters\r\n    url = f\"{base_url}?{urllib.parse.urlencode(params)}\"\r\n\r\n    try:\r\n        # Make API request\r\n        request = urllib.request.Request(url, headers={\"apikey\": api_key})\r\n        with urllib.request.urlopen(request) as response:\r\n            if response.status != 200:\r\n                raise ValueError(f\"API returned status code {response.status}\")\r\n\r\n            data = json.loads(response.read().decode(\"utf-8\"))\r\n\r\n            if not isinstance(data, list):\r\n                raise ValueError(f\"Unexpected API response format: {type(data)}\")\r\n\r\n            return data\r\n\r\n    except urllib.error.HTTPError as e:\r\n        error_body = e.read().decode(\"utf-8\") if e.fp else \"No error details\"\r\n        raise urllib.error.HTTPError(\r\n            e.url, e.code, f\"FMP API error: {e.reason}. Details: {error_body}\", e.hdrs, e.fp\r\n        )\r\n    except urllib.error.URLError as e:\r\n        raise ValueError(f\"Network error: {e.reason}\")\r\n\r\n\r\ndef validate_date_range(from_date: str, to_date: str) -> None:\r\n    \"\"\"\r\n\n[181 more lines in file. Use offset=80 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774573442090}}
{"type":"message","id":"855bcb32","parentId":"b0033461","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:04:07.620Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来脚本使用的是 `/api/v3/economic_calendar` 这个 endpoint，但 FMP 说这是一个 legacy endpoint。\n\n让我查看 FMP 的文档，看看新的经济日历 API endpoint 是什么。或者我可以直接搜索一下 FMP 的当前 API 文档。\n\n实际上，我可以先尝试用 curl 直接测试 FMP API，看看是否能找到正确的 endpoint。\n\n根据 FMP 的新文档，经济日历 API 可能已经迁移到不同的 endpoint。让我先试试 `/api/v3/economic_events` 或其他类似的 endpoint。\n\n不过，考虑到这是 trading skills 仓库，脚本应该会被更新。让我先查看一下 earnings calendar 的脚本，看看它是否也有同样的问题。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_47199286cd874ce8a8daffd0","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.claude\\skills\\claude-trading-skills\\skills\\earnings-calendar\\SKILL.md","limit":50,"offset":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":402,"output":321,"cacheRead":35267,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35990,"cost":{"input":0.00024119999999999998,"output":0.0007062,"cacheRead":0.00387937,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00482677}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774573442097}}
{"type":"message","id":"07b9c04c","parentId":"855bcb32","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:04:07.630Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_47199286cd874ce8a8daffd0","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\r\nRetrieve the current date and time:\r\n- Use system date/time to get today's date\r\n- Note: \"Today's date\" is provided in the environment (<env> tag)\r\n- Calculate the target week: Next 7 days from current date\r\n\r\n**Date Range Calculation**:\r\n```\r\nCurrent Date: [e.g., November 2, 2025]\r\nTarget Week Start: [Current Date + 1 day, e.g., November 3, 2025]\r\nTarget Week End: [Current Date + 7 days, e.g., November 9, 2025]\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Why This Matters**:\r\n- Earnings calendars are time-sensitive\r\n- \"Next week\" must be calculated from the actual current date\r\n- Provides accurate date range for API request\r\n\r\n**Format dates in YYYY-MM-DD** for API compatibility.\r\n\r\n### Step 2: Load FMP API Guide\r\n\r\nBefore retrieving data, load the comprehensive FMP API guide:\r\n\r\n```\r\nRead: references/fmp_api_guide.md\r\n```\r\n\r\nThis guide contains:\r\n- FMP API endpoint structure and parameters\r\n- Authentication requirements\r\n- Market cap filtering strategy (via Company Profile API)\r\n- Earnings timing conventions (BMO, AMC, TAS)\r\n- Response format and field descriptions\r\n- Error handling strategies\r\n- Best practices and optimization tips\r\n\r\n### Step 3: API Key Detection and Configuration\r\n\r\nDetect API key availability based on environment.\r\n\r\n**Multi-Environment API Key Detection**:\r\n\r\n#### 3.1 Check Environment Variable (CLI/Desktop)\r\n\r\n```bash\r\nif [ ! -z \"$FMP_API_KEY\" ]; then\r\n  echo \"✓ API key found in environment\"\r\n  API_KEY=$FMP_API_KEY\r\nfi\r\n\n[623 more lines in file. Use offset=100 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774573447626}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d5f21e8","parentId":"07b9c04c","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:04:11.774Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 earnings-calendar skill 也是使用 FMP API。让我检查一下 earnings calendar 的脚本，看看它是否能正常工作。\n\n实际上，由于 API endpoint 变更的问题，可能这个仓库的脚本需要更新。让我先测试一下 earnings calendar 的脚本，看看是否也有同样的问题。\n\n或者，我可以直接使用 web_search 或 web_fetch 来获取经济事件和财报信息，而不是依赖 FMP API。\n\n让我先尝试直接搜索一下最新的经济事件和财报信息，看看能否获取到数据。如果可以，我就可以设置定时提醒来定期获取这些信息。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_c90377ea39134bd6b5dd4a19","name":"web_search","arguments":{"query":"FMP economic calendar API 2025 2026 new endpoint","count":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":367,"output":258,"cacheRead":35852,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36477,"cost":{"input":0.00022019999999999999,"output":0.0005676,"cacheRead":0.00394372,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00473152}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774573447631}}
