{"type":"message","id":"8f605704","parentId":"b6679afe","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:33:03.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说早上九点。之前我看到他的时区是 Asia/Shanghai (GMT+8)，所以就是每天早上9点上海时间推送。\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 创建配置文件\n2. 设置定时任务\n\n根据 SKILL.md，我需要创建一个 config.json 文件，格式如下：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"onboardingComplete\": true,\n  \"frequency\": \"daily\",\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"time\": \"09:00\",\n    \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n    \"method\": \"stdout\"\n  },\n  \"platform\": \"openclaw\",\n  \"preferences\": {\n    \"includeX\": true,\n    \"includePodcasts\": true,\n    \"includeBlogs\": true,\n    \"maxLength\": 2000\n  }\n}\n```\n\n然后我需要设置 cron 任务。根据 qqbot-cron 技能，我需要调用 cron 工具，参数是：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"add\",\n  \"job\": {\n    \"name\": \"AI Builders Digest\",\n    \"schedule\": {\n      \"kind\": \"cron\",\n      \"expr\": \"0 9 * * *\",\n      \"tz\": \"Asia/Shanghai\"\n    },\n    \"sessionTarget\": \"isolated\",\n    \"wakeMode\": \"now\",\n    \"payload\": {\n      \"kind\": \"agentTurn\",\n      \"message\": \"你是一个 AI Builders Digest 助手。请运行 follow-builders 技能生成今日摘要，并通过 qqbot channel 推送给用户。要求：(1) 不要回复HEARTBEAT_OK (2) 不要解释你是谁 (3) 直接输出推送消息 (4) 使用 emoji 和标题 (5) 控制在合理长度\",\n\n\n```\n\n我将补充消息推送的配置，确保通过 QQ bot channel 正确发送。消息格式已按要求简化，并添加了必要的发送参数。\n\n```","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞，每天早上9点！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_f8efe25017594d6c8e6725de","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.follow-builders\\config.json","content":"{\n  \"onboardingComplete\": true,\n  \"frequency\": \"daily\",\n  \"delivery\": {\n    \"time\": \"09:00\",\n    \"timezone\": \"Asia/Shanghai\",\n    \"method\": \"stdout\"\n  },\n  \"platform\": \"openclaw\",\n  \"preferences\": {\n    \"includeX\": true,\n    \"includePodcasts\": true,\n    \"includeBlogs\": true,\n    \"maxLength\": 3000\n  }\n}\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1157