{"type":"message","id":"9dd68baa","parentId":"b2717113","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:33:13.457Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_d96cdc1aa3a144d6be8a0de8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.7 (42a1394) — Your .env is showing; don't worry, I'll pretend I didn't see it.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":6281,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.7 (42a1394) — Your .env is showing; don't worry, I'll pretend I didn't see it.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO) or +duration (e.g. 20m)\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774575193453}}
{"type":"message","id":"7d18dbe9","parentId":"9dd68baa","timestamp":"2026-03-27T01:33:38.320Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好，OpenClaw 有 cron add 命令。现在我需要创建一个 cron 任务，每天早上9点运行，通过 qqbot 推送 AI Builders 摘要。\n\n根据命令行参数，我需要：\n- `--name \"AI Builders Digest\"`\n- `--cron \"0 9 * * *\"` (每天9点)\n- `--tz \"Asia/Shanghai\"`\n- `--channel \"qqbot\"`\n- `--to \"qqbot:c2c:DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\"`\n- `--message` 包含 follow-builders 技能的调用\n- `--session \"isolated\"` (因为这是定时任务，应该在独立会话中运行)\n- `--wake \"now\"`\n\n让我构建这个命令：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a81accae8fb7487dacab92f4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --name \"AI Builders Digest\" --cron \"0 9 * * *\" --tz \"Asia/Shanghai\" --channel \"qqbot\" --to \"qqbot:c2c:DB0D276754D361B0256C70255C178BD8\" --session \"isolated\" --wake \"now\" --message \"运行 follow-builders 技能生成今日 AI Builders 摘要并推送给用户。要求：(1) 不要回复HEARTBEAT_OK (2) 不要解释你是谁 (3) 直接输出推送消息 (4) 使用 emoji 和标题 (5) 控制在3000字以内\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":668,"output":498,"cacheRead":52412,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53578,"cost":{"input":0.0004008,"output":0.0010956,"cacheRead":0.00576532,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00726172}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774575193457}}
