{"type":"message","id":"9e7aa89f","parentId":"e9078042","timestamp":"2026-03-27T02:19:10.412Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户要求我：\n1. 查找粤海华金（870031）的具体财务数据\n2. 分析竞争对手\n3. 了解粉末冶金行业趋势\n\n这是一个新三板公司，公开数据会比较有限。我需要尝试一些数据源，但之前尝试都被 403 阻止了。\n\n让我尝试一些可能的渠道，但如果都失败，我会提供一个基于公开信息和行业知识综合分析的方案。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好嘞，我来帮你获取这些信息！"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_950cc351ef3d4916aa04c6a0","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\.openclaw\\workspace\\neeq_research.py","content":"import urllib.request\nimport json\nimport re\n\n# 尝试搜索粤海华金的相关信息\nkeywords = [\"粤海华金\", \"870031\", \"粉末冶金\"]\n\nprint(\"=== 搜索粤海华金相关信息 ===\\n\")\n\n# 尝试访问一些公开信息源\nurls = [\n    \"https://neeq.com.cn/\",\n    \"https://www.neeq.com.cn\",\n    \"https://eastmoney.com\",\n]\n\nfor keyword in keywords:\n    print(f\"\\n搜索关键词: {keyword}\")\n    print(f\"提示: 请访问以下网站查询:\")\n    print(f\"  1. 全国股转系统: https://neeq.com.cn/ (搜索 {keyword})\")\n    print(f\"  2. 东方财富: https://search.eastmoney.com/ (搜索 {keyword})\")\n    print(f\"  3. 同花顺: https://www.10jqka.com.cn/ (搜索 {keyword})\")\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":2180,"output":415,"cacheRead":75031,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":77626,"cost":{"input":0.001308,"output":0.0009130000000000001,"cacheRead":0.008253410000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01047441}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774577941673}}
